description: Sabores de Mexico is serving LA a super tasty selection of organic gourmet Mexican cuisine. You'll find a flavorful variety of tostadas, burritos, enchiladas, and quesadillas (to name a few) all bursting with delicious veggies, cheese, and a protein of your choice.There’s something delicious for everyone whether you’re seeking vegetarian, vegan, or gluten-free dishes. If you like to eat pretty light, there’s also an incredible selection of Crossfit specials, including Wild Halibut Ceviche, nutritious Breakfast Bowls, and much more. Whether you call on this bright orange truck to come cater your next event or you come out for a feast on the streets, you’re sure to adore every bite from Sabores de Mexico.
name: Sabores de Mexico
